<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Job Application Sent</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">Application Sent Successfully</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>Your job application has been successfully sent!</p>
    
    <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #667eea;">Job Details</h3>
      <p><strong>Position:</strong> {{jobTitle}}</p>
      <p><strong>Company:</strong> {{companyName}}</p>
      <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
      <p><strong>Applied on:</strong> {{appliedDate}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p><strong>Documents sent:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      {{#each documents}}
        <li>{{this}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
    
    <p>The employer will review your application and contact you if they're interested.</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" style="background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 15px 40px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">View Application Status</a>
    </div>
    
    <p>Good luck with your application!</p>
    
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 30px 0;">
    
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; text-align: center;">
      © 2024 Ostora. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
